                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">TRUE:  3rd World Nation at U.S. southern border.  </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      /
                      <span>7</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-03-15</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Huntington is to be commended for writing such a great book.  As we learn in elementary school, Truth is not an opinion or a matter of interpretation.    
<br />
<br />The U.S.A. is only nation with a unguarded 2,000 border with a massive 3rd world nation.  Europe, Japan, Australia, etc are by geography separated from the 3rd world.   
<br />
<br />If you do not believe that U.S. is next a massive 3rd world nation, all you have to do is walk over the Texas or California border with Mexico.  
<br />
<br />The streets are unpaved, children sleeping on the streets, shanties towns on hills, massive over-population.   A few steps and you are crossing from a developed nation to poor, polluted, corrupt, 3rd world nation.  
<br />
<br />The simple truth is that Mexicans bring the 3rd world to the U.S.  Mexicans in U.S. have incredibly low economic, academic, and social achievements in the U.S.  
<br />
<br />The are surely NOT over-represented in colleges, medicine or Nobel Prize winners but are surely over-represented picking strawberries, working the night shift at Burger-King, McDonald and Taco Bell.  
<br />
<br />Americans are getting the 3rd world of crime, poverty, low-achievement when Mexicans bring Mexico to the U.S.
<br />
<br />Huntington avoids the one letter word at the heart of the issue:  IQ = 85.   Mexicans have an IQ centered around 85.  Fifteen points below the norm of medians of average Americans of 100.  IQ 85 versus IQ 100 can mean a great deal in terms of achievement.  
<br />
<br />IQ is fixed by Nature.  Nature made human beings and Nature endowed Mexicans with an IQ of 85.    Unpleasant but True and unlikely to change tomorrow.   
<br />
<br />Truth is not an opinion.  The U.S. is bordered by a massive, poverty-stricken 3rd world nations at its southern border.  With an IQ of 85, Mexicans bring low achievements, low level of success to U.S.  The simple quesiton is:  do you want live in the 3rd?  Do you want the U.S. to turn into a 3rd world nation?</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Hand Basket or A Hornet's Nest?</div>
                    <div>
